      "title": "Legal approval for Number Portability service",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Oshadha Senanayake, Director General of the Telecommunications Regulatory Commission, has said that all telephone subscribers have received legal approval for the Number Portability service.",
        "He mentioned this at the press conference held at the Presidential Media Center.",
        "That all telephone subscribers have received legal approval for the Number Portability service,",
        "The Director General of the Telecommunications Regulatory Commission Mr. Oshadha Senanayake made the announcement at the press conference which is now being held at the Presidential Media Centre. #lka"
